title: La lucha libre de hoy (Lucha Libre of Today)
itunes:title: La lucha libre de hoy (Lucha Libre of Today)
description:
Growing up, José Luis Hernández disliked lucha libre, the famous style of Mexican professional wrestling. So he never imagined that someday, he would be one of its biggest stars.

A transcript of this episode is available at https://bit.ly/3HjrhHh.
